---

# ⚠️ Limitations

- Intended for research purposes only
- Not validated for clinical diagnosis
- Performance depends on dataset diversity
- Caption quality may decrease on highly complex polymicrobial smears
- BLIP-2 requires substantial GPU memory
- Quantized model loading is recommended for consumer GPUs

